SmoodersBoard is a simply proof of concept of what you can do with smoodit (http://smood.it) ruby gem.

SmooderBoard class can be used to have a leaderboard of your followers/followings smooders based on their moods, i.e. a smoodsboard.
The test_me.rb example requires your smoodit username an prints out your followings and followers smoodsboars.

Have fun!

== Usage Example ==

ruby test_me.rb foo
